---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
const updated = '2026-04-13';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Al Sham Palace Auto Car Service Abu Dhabi"
  description="Privacy Policy for Al Sham Palace Auto Car Service. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="bg-dark-900 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-500">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone-500">Last updated: {updated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-editorial space-y-8 text-stone-400">

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">{business.name}</strong> ("we", "our", "us") operates the website <a href={business.website} class="text-brand-400">{business.website}</a>. We are a car service business located at {business.address.street}, {business.address.city}, Abu Dhabi, UAE. Contact us at <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`} class="text-brand-400">{business.email}</a> or call <a href={business.phoneHref} class="text-brand-400">{business.phone}</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">We collect information you provide directly when you:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Fill in our contact form (name, phone number, email, service needed, location, message)</li>
            <li>Call or WhatsApp us directly</li>
            <li>Visit our workshop in person</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We also automatically collect standard website analytics data (pages visited, device type, approximate location) through Google Tag Manager and Google Analytics.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>To respond to your service enquiry and provide a quote</li>
            <li>To book and fulfil the requested car service</li>
            <li>To contact you about your service booking or follow up</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services using aggregated analytics data</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do <strong class="text-white">not</strong> sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Our website uses the following third-party services:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Google Tag Manager / Google Analytics</strong> — website traffic analytics</li>
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Web3Forms</strong> — contact form submission processing</li>
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Google Maps</strong> — location display and directions</li>
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">WhatsApp</strong> — customer communication (via external link)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Each of these services has its own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing them if you have concerns.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">We retain contact form submissions and customer records for up to 2 years for service history and accounting purposes. Analytics data is retained per Google Analytics default settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">You have the right to request access to, correction, or deletion of any personal data we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`} class="text-brand-400">{business.email}</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">Our website uses cookies placed by Google Analytics and Google Tag Manager for analytics purposes. These are not used for advertising. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-white">8. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">For any privacy-related questions, contact us:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-none space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`} class="text-brand-400">{business.email}</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Phone:</strong> <a href={business.phoneHref} class="text-brand-400">{business.phone}</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-stone-300">Address:</strong> {business.address.street}, {business.address.city}, Abu Dhabi, UAE</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
